2021年4月11日，20岁的[[非裔美国人|非裔美国]]男子'''丹特·莱特'''（{{lang-en|Daunte Wright}}）在美国[[明尼蘇達州|明尼蘇達州]]明尼阿波利斯-圣保罗都会区的一次交通拦截中，被明尼苏达州布鲁克林中心的警察金柏莉·波特（Kimberly Potter）开枪射杀<ref name="st_first_article">{{Cite news |last=Klecker |first=Mara |last2=Hyatt |first2=Kim |last3=Sawyer |first3=Liz |last4=Mannix |first4=Andy |date=2021-04-12 |title=Brooklyn Center police fatally shoot man, 20, inflaming tensions during the Derek Chauvin trial |language= |work=Star Tribune |location=Minneapolis, Minnesota |url=https://www.startribune.com/brooklyn-center-police-fatally-shoot-man-20-inflaming-tensions-during-the-derek-chauvin-trial/600044821/ |dead-url=no |access-date=2021-04-14 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210412211625/https://www.startribune.com/brooklyn-center-police-fatally-shoot-man-20-inflaming-tensions-during-the-derek-chauvin-trial/600044821/ |archive-date=2021-04-12 }}</ref><ref name="bodycamvideo">{{Cite news |date=2021-04-12 |title=Brooklyn Center police body camera footage captures fatal shooting of Daunte Wright |language= |work=KARE-TV |publisher=Tenga |agency=NBC |location=Minneapolis, Minnesota |url=https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=cdv03O23vRQt=30 |dead-url=no |access-date=2021-04-14 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210412192631/https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=cdv03O23vRQ |archive-date=2021-04-12 |via=YouTube }}</ref><ref name="POTTERIDSTAR">{{cite news |last1=Walsh |first1=Paul |last2=Sawyer |first2=Liz |title=Officer who fatally shot man in Brooklyn Center is identified as 26-year veteran |url=https://www.startribune.com/officer-who-fatally-shot-man-in-brooklyn-center-is-identified-as-26-year-veteran/600045243/ |access-date=2021-04-13 |publisher=Star Tribune |date=2021-04-12 |archive-date=2021-04-13 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210413135703/https://www.startribune.com/officer-who-fatally-shot-man-in-brooklyn-center-is-identified-as-26-year-veteran/600045243/ }}</ref>。赖特在中枪后继续驾驶汽车行驶了几个街区，然后与另一辆车相撞，并撞上了水泥障碍物。他当场被宣布死亡<ref name="nyt-homicide">{{cite web|author1=The New York Times|date=2021-04-12|title=What to Know About the Police Shooting of Daunte Wright|url=https://www.nytimes.com/article/daunte-wright-death-minnesota.html|access-date=2021-04-13|website=The New York Times|quote=The Hennepin County medical examiner concluded Monday that Mr. Wright 'died of a gunshot wound of the chest and manner of death is homicide.'|archive-date=2021-04-12|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210412235340/https://www.nytimes.com/article/daunte-wright-death-minnesota.html}}</ref>。

第二天，警方表示波特本想使用[[泰瑟|泰瑟]]枪，但却不小心拿起了手枪，一枪击中了赖特的胸部<ref name="CBSNews13April">{{cite web |last1=Dakss |first1=Brian |last2=Sundby |first2=Alex |last3=Freiman |first3=Jordan |title=Second night of unrest after fatal police shooting of Daunte Wright outside Minneapolis |url=https://www.cbsnews.com/live-updates/daunte-wright-killed-police-brooklyn-center-minnesota-protests-second-night/ |website=CBS News |publisher=cbsnews.com |access-date=2021-04-13 |date=2021-04-13 |archive-date=2021-04-13 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210413063748/https://www.cbsnews.com/live-updates/daunte-wright-killed-police-brooklyn-center-minnesota-protests-second-night/ }}</ref><ref name="MedicalExaminer">{{cite web |title=Medical examiner declares Daunte Wright death a homicide |url=https://kstp.com/minnesota-news/20-year-old-daunte-wright-shot-killed-traffic-stop-crash-brooklyn-center-police-overnight-unrest-curfew/6072395/ |website=KSTP |publisher=kstp.com |access-date=2021-04-13 |language= |date=2021-04-12 |archive-date=2021-04-13 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210413015831/https://kstp.com/minnesota-news/20-year-old-daunte-wright-shot-killed-traffic-stop-crash-brooklyn-center-police-overnight-unrest-curfew/6072395/ }}</ref>。枪击案发生两天后，波特和布鲁克林中心警察局长蒂姆·坎农（Tim Gannon）辞职<ref name="PotterGannonResign">{{cite web |last1=Shapiro |first1=Emily |title=Officer who shot, killed Daunte Wright and Brooklyn Center police chief both resign |url=https://abcnews.go.com/US/police-officer-shot-killed-daunte-wright-resigns/story?id=77048421 |website=ABC News |publisher=abcnews.go.com |access-date=2021-04-13 |language= |date=2021-04-13 |archive-date=2021-04-13 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210413173933/https://abcnews.go.com/US/police-officer-shot-killed-daunte-wright-resigns/story?id=77048421 }}</ref>。

这起枪击事件引发了布鲁克林中心的抗议活动，并在[[明尼阿波利斯-聖保羅都會區|明尼阿波利斯-聖保羅都會區]]再次引发了针对[[警察暴力|警察暴力]]的持续性示威，导致全市和地区性的宵禁<ref name="Curfews">{{cite web |last1=Gottfried |first1=Mara |title=Hundreds ignore curfew to protest Daunte Wright shooting outside Brooklyn Center P.D. |url=https://www.msn.com/en-us/news/us/nighttime-curfew-going-into-effect-in-ramsey-hennepin-anoka-counties-after-brooklyn-center-officer-fatally-shoots-man/ar-BB1fzUzC |publisher=msn.com |access-date=2021-04-13 |language= |date=2021-04-12 |archive-date=2021-04-12 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210412223631/https://www.msn.com/en-us/news/us/nighttime-curfew-going-into-effect-in-ramsey-hennepin-anoka-counties-after-brooklyn-center-officer-fatally-shoots-man/ar-BB1fzUzC }}</ref>。示威活动也蔓延到了美国各地城市<ref name="ProtestsGrow">{{cite web |last1=Sullivan |first1=Becky |title=Protests Grow In Minnesota And Around U.S. Over Death of Daunte Wright |url=https://www.npr.org/2021/04/13/986764183/protests-grow-in-minnesota-and-around-u-s-over-death-of-daunte-wright |website=NPR |publisher=npr.org |access-date=2021-04-13 |language= |date=2021-04-13 |archive-date=2021-04-13 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210413181038/https://www.npr.org/2021/04/13/986764183/protests-grow-in-minnesota-and-around-u-s-over-death-of-daunte-wright }}</ref>。

== 当事人 ==
===丹特·莱特===
丹特·莱特（Daunte Wright）是一名20岁的[[非裔美国人|非裔美国]]男子<ref>{{cite web |last1=Sullivan |first1=Becky |last2=Romo |first2=Vanessa |title=Officer Who Fatally Shot Daunte Wright With 'Accidental Discharge' Is Identified |url=https://www.npr.org/2021/04/12/986458941/police-say-accidental-discharge-of-gun-led-to-daunte-wrights-death |website=NPR |publisher=npr.org |access-date=2021-04-13 |language= |date=2021-04-12 |archive-date=2021-04-12 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210412222453/https://www.npr.org/2021/04/12/986458941/police-say-accidental-discharge-of-gun-led-to-daunte-wrights-death }}</ref>

===金·波特===
枪击事件发生时，48岁的[[美國白人|美國白人]]女子金·波特（Kim Potter）是布鲁克林中心警察局的警察<ref name="POTTERIDSTAR"/><ref name="PotterBio">{{cite web |last1=McEvoy |first1=Jemima |title=Here’s What We Know About Kim Potter, The Minnesota Officer Who Shot Daunte Wright |url=https://www.forbes.com/sites/jemimamcevoy/2021/04/13/heres-what-we-know-about-kim-potter-the-minnesota-officer-who-shot-daunte-wright/?sh=21b124f37fd2 |website=Forbes |publisher=forbes.com |access-date=2021-04-13 |language= |date=2021-04-13 |archive-date=2021-04-13 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210413225031/https://www.forbes.com/sites/jemimamcevoy/2021/04/13/heres-what-we-know-about-kim-potter-the-minnesota-officer-who-shot-daunte-wright/?sh=21b124f37fd2 }}</ref><ref name="one">{{cite news |last=Navratil |first=Liz |last2=Mannix |first2=Andy |title=Chief: Officer meant to use Taser, not firearm, on Daunte Wright |date=2021-04-12 |work=Star Tribune |location=Minneapolis, Minnesota |url=https://www.startribune.com/chief-officer-may-have-meant-to-use-taser-not-firearm-on-daunte-wright/600045076/ |dead-url=no |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210413173714/https://www.startribune.com/police-chief-officer-meant-to-use-taser-not-firearm-on-daunte-wright-brooklyn-center-shooting/600045076/ |archive-date=2021-04-13 |language= |accessdate=2021-04-14 }}</ref><ref>{{cite web |last1=Ibrahim |first1=Mohamed |last2=Householder |first2=Mike |title=Daunte Wright shooting: Police officer Kim Potter, Chief Tom Gannon resign from Brooklyn Center Police Department |url=https://abc7.com/daunte-wright-death-minnesota-traffic-stop-shooting-brooklyn-center-video/10511641/ |website=ABC7 |publisher=abc7.com |access-date=2021-04-13 |language= |date=2021-04-13 |archive-date=2021-04-13 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210413183103/https://abc7.com/daunte-wright-death-minnesota-traffic-stop-shooting-brooklyn-center-video/10511641/ }}</ref>，她自1995年起就在该警察局工作<ref name="POTTERIDSTAR"/><ref name="PotterBio"/>。

